  drm/stm: dsi: use new SYSTEM_SLEEP_PM_OPS() macro
  drm/stm: dsi: expose DSI PHY internal clock
  arm: dts: st: fix DSI peripheral clock on stm32mp15 boards

Yannick Fertre (1):
  drm/stm: dsi: add pm runtime ops

